            workspace 139e7cdc-... + 100 composio_poll_state rows
            (toolkit='loadtest', next_poll_at=now()-1s).
  T+0:26  - First sweep (02:43:07): scanned=100 failed=30
            throttled=70 chain_depth=0 (test ran while H.5 cap
            was still =30; observed throttling exactly as H.5
